        Viking on <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Mars: Been There, Tried That</ENAMEX>
        The <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Viking</ENAMEX> missions to <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Mars</ENAMEX> in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the late 1970s</TIMEX> were the <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</NUMEX> (and as yet, the only)
