        of any organic molecules in the soil at level of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</NUMEX> part per <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">billion</NUMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Biemann 1979).</ENAMEX> It is
